General.Name: Intermail A/S
General.Description: InterMail A/S provides paper-based marketing communication in the Nordic region and rest of Europe. It offers lead generation, customer communication, and customer loyalty solutions; and e-mail marketing, marketing automation, letter, emails, special solution, SMS, social media, google ads, gamification, SEO, and direct mail services. The company also provides IM Loyalty, RelationPlus, direct mail, and e-box solutions. The company was formerly known as National Industri A/S and changed its name to InterMail A/S in 2004. InterMail A/S was incorporated in 1972 and is based in Hvidovre, Denmark.
